summary: A tiny mod that adds a garden of alchemical ingredients and ornamental plants to the front of the house Severin Manor in Raven Rock. Requires Dragonborn, obviously.
descriptionHtml:
This is a tiny mod that adds a garden of alchemical ingredients and ornamental plants to the front of the house Severin Manor in Raven Rock.The plants added are a nice mix of Skyrim- and Morrowind-native flora.

Requires Dragonborn, obviously.Â  This mod will not clash with other mods that alter Severin Manor, but may have issues with mods that alter Raven Rock.

To install manually, place both files in the .zip in your Skyrim/data directory.
author: Vigliant1000
